6. All user messages:
   - "see our last work"
   - "analize it in deep to understand the loginc, structure,files"
   - "/frontend-design:frontend-design" (skill invocation)
   - "analize deeper to be able to offer the most creative, innovative and inteligent sollution"

7. Pending Tasks:
   - Provide deeper analysis for more creative, innovative, and intelligent frontend design solutions
   - No specific implementation task has been selected yet - user is still in exploration/analysis phase

8. Current Work:
   The immediate work before this summary request was providing frontend design analysis and recommendations for the CortexBuild Ultimate platform. After reading the design-related files (src/index.css, src/components/layout/Header.tsx, src/components/auth/LoginPage.tsx), I provided:

   - Analysis of existing design strengths (typography hierarchy, blueprint aesthetic, amber-dominant palette, micro-interaction system)
   - Identification of opportunities for enhancement
