   167→            ))}
   168→          </div>
   169→
   170→          <div className="rounded-2xl border border-gray-800 bg-gray-900 p-5">
   171→            <h3 className="mb-4 text-sm font-semibold text-white">Revenue vs Cost vs Profit</h3>
